==Useful Info==
'''Hogs''' are rare and delicious animals.

==Tips & Tricks==
Although they are no threat on their own, their presence in a herd invariably means that [[Kirke]] is nearby. In the early [[Dungeon]], they might also be part of a butcher's [[vault]]. A solo, wandering hog might be indicative of a [[shapeshifter (monster)|shapeshifter]].
